								<div class="site-info">
									<h3 class="site-title">My Moroccan Food </h3>
							    <div data-content-field="site-description" class="site-description"><p>Moroccan food blog. Moroccan cooking made simple and easy.&nbsp;Modern Moroccan,&nbsp;recipes, cuisine and dishes. &nbsp;Traditional Moroccan recipes and Moroccan inspired recipes. Tagine, couscous, bastila, appetizers, pastries, deserts recipes and more. Facts about ingredients, spices and Moroccan cuisine culture.</p></div>
